videos.description: Bryant Crawford gets an extra pass from Brandon Childress and gets the deep-ball to fall for the Demon Deacons.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Crawford sinks corner 3

videos.description: Doral Moore gets the lob from Brandon Childress and finishes strong with two hands.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Moore slams home alley-oop

videos.description: Olivier Sarr throws down the alley-oop with authority for the Demon Deacons in the second half.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Sarr stuffs in alley-oop

videos.description: Keyshawn Woods blows by his defender with a nifty move and lays it in for Wake Forest.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Woods attacks the rack

videos.description: Gabe DeVoe sprints past his defender and gets a pretty floater to fall for the Tigers in the second half.
videos.headline: Clemson's DeVoe drops in floater

videos.description: Marcquise Reed comes off a high screen and drills the midrange shot late in the second half for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Clemson's Reed knocks down dagger
